  <div class="instruction-text">
    <h2>How to convert Excel or CSV files to PDF</h2>
    <p>Follow these easy steps to convert spreadsheets into PDFs:</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
    <p><b>1.</b> Click the "Select a file" button above, or drag and drop a spreadsheet file into the drop zone.</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
    <p><b>2.</b> Choose the XLS, XLSX, or CSV file you want to convert.</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
    <p><b>3.</b> Watch as Docflex automatically converts your file into a PDF.</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
    <p><b>4.</b> Download your new PDF, or sign in to share it.</p>
    <hr class="hr-tag">
  </div>
  <div class="instruction-img">
    <!-- You can add an image of Excel to PDF conversion here -->
  </div>
</div>

